org.jscsi.parser

Class MessageParserFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jscsi.parser.MessageParserFactory

  • public final class MessageParserFactory
extends Object

    MessageParserFactory

    This class creates a specified parser object. But only one object of this kind. With this technique it minimizes the object creation process and affect the execution speed, too.

    Author:
    Volker Wildi, University of Konstanz
